OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773004304
OL,3,CKnife-wielding burglar broke into home
OL,4,Cand attacked man while he slept
OL,6,FA burglar who broke into a home, armed
OL,7,Fwith a knife, and attacked a man while
OL,8,Fhe slept, has been jailed.
OL,10,FIn the early hours of 7 August, 2025,
OL,11,Fofficers were called to an address in
OL,12,FCenturion Close, Salisbury, following
OL,13,Fa report that a man had been woken by
OL,14,Fsomeone trying to attack him.
OL,16,FThe victim was left with a bruised
OL,17,Fface and cuts after trying to retrieve
OL,18,Fthe knife from the burglar and then
OL,19,Fjumped onto a balcony and on to the
OL,20,Fground to escape.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
