PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773004304
OL,3,CKnife-wielding burglar broke into home
OL,4,Cand attacked man while he slept
OL,6,FJoshua McMenamin, 32, of Friary Lane,
OL,7,FSalisbury, appeared at Winchester
OL,8,FCrown Court on Thursday (5 March) and
OL,9,Fwas jailed for five years and seven
OL,10,Fmonths after pleading guilty to
OL,11,Faggravated burglary.
OL,13,FThe victim, who knew his attacker,
OL,14,Fsaid in a statement: "This incident
OL,15,Fhas shaken me up. I am now extremely
OL,16,Fanxious at night.
OL,18,F"This is something that now keeps me
OL,19,Fawake at night, as I know that I might
OL,20,Fwake up and see him in my room again.
OL,21,FIt really scares me."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773004304
OL,3,CKnife-wielding burglar broke into home
OL,4,Cand attacked man while he slept
OL,6,FPC Charlie Forster said: "This was a
OL,7,Fterrifying and traumatic experience
OL,8,Ffor the victim, who was woken in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the night to find an
OL,10,Fintruder who we now know was
OL,11,FMcMenamin, armed with a knife.
OL,13,F"When officers arrived at the scene,
OL,14,Fthey located a knife as well as a safe
OL,15,Fwhich was located outside the property
OL,16,F` it is believed McMenamin was
OL,17,Fattempting to make off with the
OL,18,Fcontents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773004304
OL,3,CKnife-wielding burglar broke into home
OL,4,Cand attacked man while he slept
OL,6,F"The victim has described the impact
OL,7,Fthis incident has had on him, and this
OL,8,Fis totally unacceptable. Nobody should
OL,9,Fface this kind of fear in what should
OL,10,Fbe the safety of their home and I am
OL,11,Fpleased that a custodial sentence has
OL,12,Fbeen given."
OL,14,FAs well as the custodial sentence,
OL,15,FMcMenamin must also pay a surcharge of
OL,16,F#228.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
